<!--NOTE: Please do not change the lead sentence(s) without consulting the discussion page first. The lead sentence has been discussed and there is general consensus that this is the best one for now. Thanks.-->
[[File:Milky_Way_IR_Spitzer.jpg|thumb]]拍摄的银河系中心图象]]

'''銀河星系'''（古稱'''银河'''、'''天河'''、'''星河'''、'''天汉'''、'''銀漢'''等）<ref>{{cite web|url=http://hb.xinhuanet.com/zhibo/2010-08/04/content_20528979.htm|title=鄖西是“牛郎織女”相會之地|work=xinhuanet.com|deadurl=yes|archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20160808140401/http://hb.xinhuanet.com/zhibo/2010-08/04/content_20528979.htm|archivedate=2016-08-08}}</ref>，是一個包含[[太陽系|太陽系]]<ref>{{cite web|title=Our Solar System: Overview: Our Galactic Neighborhood |publisher=NASA |url=http://solarsystem.nasa.gov/planets/solarsystem |deadurl=no |archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20161127080545/https://solarsystem.nasa.gov/planets/solarsystem |archivedate=2016-11-27 }}</ref>的[[棒旋星系|棒旋星系]]。直徑介於100,000<ref>{{cite web |author=Elizabeth Howell |url=http://www.universetoday.com/75691/how-big-is-the-milky-way/ |title=How Big Is The Milky Way? |date=2015-01-20 |publisher=[[Universe_Today|Universe Today]] |archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20141015234530/http://www.universetoday.com/75691/how-big-is-the-milky-way/ |archivedate=2014-10-15 }}</ref>至180,000光年<ref name="rpi2015">{{cite press release |author=Mary L. Martialay |title=The Corrugated Galaxy—Milky Way May Be Much Larger Than Previously Estimated |url=http://news.rpi.edu/content/2015/03/09/rippling-milky-way-may-be-much-larger-previously-estimated |date=2015-03-11 |publisher=[[Rensselaer_Polytechnic_Institute|Rensselaer Polytechnic Institute]] |archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20150313123405/http://news.rpi.edu/content/2015/03/09/rippling-milky-way-may-be-much-larger-previously-estimated |archivedate=2015-03-13}}</ref>。大約擁有1,000億至4,000億顆[[恆星|恆星]]<ref>{{cite web |title=Milky Way |url=http://www.bbc.co.uk/science/space/universe/key_places/milky_way |publisher=[[BBC|BBC]] |archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20120302071454/http://www.bbc.co.uk/science/space/universe/key_places/milky_way |archivedate=2012-03-02 }}</ref><ref>{{cite web|url=http://asd.gsfc.nasa.gov/blueshift/index.php/2015/07/22/how-many-stars-in-the-milky-way/ |title=How Many Stars in the Milky Way? |work=NASA Blueshift |deadurl=no |archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20160125140109/http://asd.gsfc.nasa.gov/blueshift/index.php/2015/07/22/how-many-stars-in-the-milky-way/ |archivedate=2016-01-25 }}</ref>，並可能有1,000億顆[[行星|行星]]<ref name="Nature-20120111" /><ref name="Space-20130102">{{cite web |author=Staff |title=100 Billion Alien Planets Fill Our Milky Way Galaxy: Study |url=http://www.space.com/19103-milky-way-100-billion-planets.html |date=2013-01-02 |publisher=[[Space.com|Space.com]] |accessdate=2013-01-03 |archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20130103060601/http://www.space.com/19103-milky-way-100-billion-planets.html |archivedate=2013-01-03 }}</ref>。太陽系距離[[銀心|銀河中心]]約24,000至28,000光年，在有著濃密氣體和塵埃，被稱為[[獵戶臂|獵戶臂]]的螺旋臂的內側邊緣。在太陽的位置，公轉週期大約是2億4,000萬年<ref name="sparke_gallagher" />。從地球看，因為是從盤狀結構的內部向外觀看，因此銀河系呈現在[[天球|天球]]上環繞一圈的帶狀。

銀河系中最古老的恆星幾乎和宇宙本身一樣古老，因此可能是在[[大爆炸|大爆炸]]之後不久的[[宇宙年表#黑暗時期|黑暗時期]]形成的<ref name=HD_140283_(arXiv)>{{cite journal |title=HD 140283: A Star in the Solar Neighborhood that Formed Shortly After the Big Bang |date=2013-02-13 |author1=H.E. Bond |display-authors=4 |author2=E. P. Nelan |author3=D. A. VandenBerg |author4=G. H. Schaefer |author5=D. Harmer |doi=10.1088/2041-8205/765/1/L12 |journal=The Astrophysical Journal |volume=765 |pages=L12 |issue=1 |arxiv=1302.3180|bibcode = 2013ApJ...765L..12B }}</ref>。在核心約10京的範圍內的恆星形成[[核球_(星系)|核球]]，並有著一或多根棒從核球向外輻射。最中心處被標示為強烈的電波源，可能是個[[超大質量黑洞|超大質量黑洞]]，被命名為[[人馬座A*|人馬座A*]]。在很大距離範圍內的恆星和氣體都以每秒大約220公里的速度在軌道上繞著銀河中心運行。這種恆定的速度違反了[[开普勒行星運動定律|开普勒動力學]]，因而認為銀河系中有大量不會輻射或吸收[[電磁輻射|電磁輻射]]的[[質量|質量]]。這些質量被稱為''[[暗物質|暗物質]]''<ref name=Koupelis_Kuhn2007 />。

銀河系有幾個[[銀河系的衛星星系|衛星星系]]，它們都是[[本星系群|本星系群]]的成員，並且是[[室女超星系團|室女超星系團]]的一部分；而它又是組成[[拉尼亞凱亞超星系團|拉尼亞凱亞超星系團]]的一部分<ref>{{cite web |publisher=youtube.com |url = https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=rENyyRwxpHo |title=Laniakea: Our home supercluster |deadurl=no |archiveurl = https://web.archive.org/web/20140904162040/http://www.youtube.com/watch?v=rENyyRwxpHo |archivedate=2014-09-04 }}</ref><ref>{{cite journal | display-authors=1 | first1=R. Brent | last1=Tully | first2=Hélène | last2=Courtois | first3=Yehuda | last3=Hoffman | first4=Daniel | last4=Pomarède | date=2014-09-04 | title=The Laniakea supercluster of galaxies | volume=513 | pages=71–73 |doi = 10.1038/0nature13674 | bibcode = 2014Natur.513...71T | issue=7516 | arxiv = 1409.0880 | journal=Nature |pmid=25186900 }}</ref>。

== 外觀 ==
[[File:Milky_Way_Night_Sky_Black_Rock_Desert_Nevada.jpg|thumb]]不受光汙染的[[黑岩沙漠|黑岩沙漠]]看見的在[[人馬座|人馬座]]方向上的銀河（包括[[銀心|銀河中心]]）。在右下方是[[天蝎座|天蝎座]]，位於[[心宿二|心宿二]]上方的亮星是[[木星|木星]]。]]

[[File:Following_the_Milky_Way_over_ALMA.webm|thumb]]上空盤旋的銀河。]]

''銀河''的某些地區可以看作是寬約30度的弧，畫過天空的朦朧光帶<ref name=pasachoff1994/>。然而，[[肉眼|肉眼]]在天空各處看見的個別恆星，全都是銀河系的一部分<ref>{{cite book| first1=H. A. | last1=Rey | title=The Stars |page = 145 | year = 1976 | isbn= 0395248302 | publisher= Houghton Mifflin Harcourt}}</ref><ref>{{cite book |title=The Cosmos: Astronomy in the New Millennium |first1=Jay M. |last1=Pasachoff |first2=Alex |last2=Filippenko |year=2013 |publisher=Cambridge University Press |page=384 |url=https://books.google.com/books?id=tZsoAAAAQBAJ&pg=PA384&dq=%22the+milky+way+itself%22+galaxy&hl=en&sa=X&ved=0ahUKEwiejvT5lv7QAhVLQSYKHTzPAYQQ6AEIODAG#v=onepage&q=%22the%20milky%20way%20itself%22%20galaxy&f=false |access-date=2017-07-29 |archive-date=2017-12-02 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20171202231358/https://books.google.com/books?id=tZsoAAAAQBAJ&pg=PA384&dq=%22the+milky+way+itself%22+galaxy&hl=en&sa=X&ved=0ahUKEwiejvT5lv7QAhVLQSYKHTzPAYQQ6AEIODAG#v=onepage&q=%22the%20milky%20way%20itself%22%20galaxy&f=false |dead-url=no }}</ref>。來自這條帶狀弧上的光，都是源自[[銀河平面|銀河平面]]上，肉眼[[角解析度|不能解析]]的恆星和其它天體累積的光亮。黑暗的區域，像是[[大裂縫_(天文學)|大裂縫]]和[[煤袋星雲|煤袋星雲]]，是來自遙遠恆星的光被[[星際塵埃|星際塵埃]]遮蔽的區域。天空中被銀河遮蔽的區域稱為[[隱帶|隱帶]]。

銀河有著相對較低的[[面亮度|面亮度]]。它的可見度會被背景光，像是[[光汙染|光汙染]]或是來自[[月球|月球]]的雜散光，大大的降低。需要每平方秒的亮度比20.2[[星等|星等]]更黑暗的天空才能清楚的看見銀河<ref>{{cite journal | doi = 10.1093/mnras/stu992  | last1=Crumey | first1=Andrew | title= Human contrast threshold and astronomical visibility | journal=Monthly Notices of the Royal Astronomical Society | date=2014 | volume=442 | pages=2600–2619 | bibcode=2014MNRAS.442.2600C | arxiv = 1405.4209 }}</ref>。當肉眼可見的[[極限星等|極限星等]]大約在+5.1等可以看見銀河，或更好的+6.1等，就可以看見許多的細節<ref name="steinicke_sakiel2007" />。這使得在明亮的都市或郊區很難看見銀河，但當月球在地平線下時，在沒有光汙染的鄉村地區看見的銀河就非常明顯{{NoteTag|name="bortle"}}。新的[[世界地圖|世界地圖]]顯示夜晚天空的人造光源亮度，由於[[光汙染|光汙染]]的緣故，地球上超過三分之一的人不能在家園看見銀河<ref>{{cite journal |last=Falchi |first=Fabio |last2=Cinzano |first2=Pierantonio |last3=Duriscoe |first3=Dan |last4=Kyba |first4=Christopher C. M. |last5=Elvidge |first5=Christopher D. |last6=Baugh |first6=Kimberly |last7=Portnov |first7=Boris A. |last8=Rybnikova |first8=Nataliya A. |last9=Furgoni |first9=Riccardo |date=2016-06-01 |title=The new world atlas of artificial night sky brightness |url = http://advances.sciencemag.org/content/2/6/e1600377 |journal=Science Advances |language=en |volume=2 |issue=6 |page = e1600377 |doi = 10.1126/sciadv.1600377 |issn=2375-2548 |pmc=4928945 |pmid=27386582 |deadurl=no |archiveurl = https://web.archive.org/web/20160711121713/http://advances.sciencemag.org/content/2/6/e1600377 |archivedate=2016-07-11 }}</ref>。

從地球觀看，銀河系可見的盤面區域涵蓋的面積包括天空中的30個[[星座|星座]]{{NoteTag|銀河的中心位於[[人馬座|人馬座]]的方向上。從人馬座，朦朦朧朧的白色光帶似乎向西通過[[天蠍座|天蠍座]]、[[天壇座|天壇座]]、[[矩尺座|矩尺座]]、[[南三角座|南三角座]]、[[圓規座|圓規座]]、[[半人馬座|半人馬座]]、[[蒼蠅座|蒼蠅座]]、[[南十字座|南十字座]]、[[船底座|船底座]]、[[船帆座|船帆座]]、[[船尾座|船尾座]]、[[大犬座|大犬座]]、[[麒麟座|麒麟座]]、[[獵戶座|獵戶座]]、[[雙子座|雙子座]]、[[金牛座|金牛座]]，到在[[御夫座|御夫座]]的[[反銀心|反銀心]]。從那兒再經過[[英仙座|英仙座]]、[[仙女座|仙女座]]、[[仙后座|仙后座]]、[[仙王座|仙王座]]、[[蝎虎座|蝎虎座]]、[[天鵝座|天鵝座]]、[[狐狸座|狐狸座]]、[[天箭座|天箭座]]、[[天鷹座|天鷹座]]、[[盾牌座|盾牌座]]，返回到[[人馬座|人馬座]]。}}。[[銀心|銀河中心]]是銀河最亮的區域，其方向在[[人馬座|人馬座]]。從人馬座，朦朧的白色光帶似乎傳遞到[[反銀心|反銀心]]所在的[[御夫座|御夫座]]。光帶然後繼續其餘的路徑回到人馬座附近，將[[天球|天球]]分成兩個大致相等的[[天球|半球]]。

銀河盤面相對於[[黃道|黃道]]（地球繞太陽公轉軌道的平面）傾斜約60度。相對於[[天球赤道|天球赤道]]，它向北遠達[[仙后座|仙后座]]，向南則抵達[[南十字座|南十字座]]，顯示地球的[[赤道|赤道平面]]和黃道相對於銀河盤面都有很大的傾斜。銀河北極位於[[赤經|赤經]] 12<sup>h</sup> 49<sup>m</sup>，[[赤緯|赤緯]] +27.4°（[[曆元|B1950]]），靠近[[周鼎一|周鼎一]]（后髮座β）；銀河南極在[[玉夫座α|玉夫座α]]附近。由於這種高傾斜度，在一年中不同的時間，銀河的弧出現在天空中的位置可以很高，也可以在很低。在地球上的北緯65度到南緯65度之間，銀河會一天經過觀測者的天頂兩次。

[[File:Milky_Way_Arch.jpg|thumb]]的[[帕瑞納天文台|帕瑞納天文台]]使用[[魚眼鏡頭|魚眼]]拍攝的拼接全景图。明亮的木星位於[[人馬座|人馬座]]，銀河的北朝下。）]]

== 大小和質量 ==
[[File:UGC_12158.jpg|thumb]]的照片。這是被認為是在外觀上最類似於銀河系的星系。|300px]]

銀河系是[[本星系群|本星系群]]第二大的星系，恆星盤面的直徑大約{{convert|100000|ly|kpc|abbr=on|sigfig=1}}，平均厚度大約{{convert|1000|ly|kpc|1|abbr=on|sigfig=1}}<ref name="ask-astro"/><ref name="Rix_Bovy">{{cite journal | last1=Rix | first1=Hans-Walter | last2=Bovy | first2=Jo | title= The Milky Way's Stellar Disk  | journal= The Astronomy and Astrophysics Review | date=2013 | volume= 21| arxiv=1301.3168 | doi=10.1007/s00159-013-0061-8 | bibcode=2013A&ARv..21...61R }}</ref>。作為有形的銀河系大小規模比較，如果[[太陽|太陽]]到[[海王星|海王星]]的大小相當於25分的美金硬幣（{{convert|0.955|in|mm|abbr=on|order=flip}}），銀河系的大小則有如美國大陸<ref>{{cite web|url=http://www.cfa.harvard.edu/seuforum/howfar/across.html |work=NASA-Smithsonian Education Forum on the Structure and Evolution of the Universe, at the Harvard Smithsonian Center for Astrophysics |accessdate=2013-03-13 |title=How Big is Our Universe: How far is it across the Milky Way? |deadurl=no |archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20130305005817/http://www.cfa.harvard.edu/seuforum/howfar/across.html |archivedate=2013-03-05 }}</ref>。蕩漾在銀河平坦的盤面上下方，像環狀細絲包圍環繞著銀河系的恆星，可能都屬於銀河系的本身<ref name="rpi2015" />。如果是這樣，這意味著銀河系的直徑在 {{convert|150,000–180,000|ly|kpc}}<ref>{{cite journal | display-authors=1 | last1=Newberg | first1=Heidi Jo | last2=Xu | first2=Yan | last3=Carlin | first3=Jeffrey L. | last4=Liu | first4=Chao | last5=Deng | first5=Licai | last6=Li | first6=Jing | last7=Schoenrich | first7=Ralph | last8=Yanny | first8=Brian | date=2015-03-01 | title=Rings and Radial Waves in the Disk of the Milky Way | journal=[[The_Astrophysical_Journal|The Astrophysical Journal]] | volume=801 | issue=2 | doi=10.1088/0004-637X/801/2/105 | arxiv=1503.00257 | bibcode=2015ApJ...801..105X | pages=105 }}</ref>。

[[File:Milky_way_profile.svg|left]]

估計的銀河系質量各不相同，取決於使用的方法和資料。最低的估計值範圍，銀河系的質量是5.8{{e|11}} [[太陽質量|太陽質量]]（{{solar mass}}），略小於[[仙女座星系|仙女座星系]]的質量<ref name="Karachentsevetal2006"/><ref name="mass"/><ref name="galmass"/>。在2009年，使用[[超長基線陣列|超長基線陣列]]發現在銀河系外側邊緣的恆星速度達到{{convert|254|km/s|mph|abbr=on}}<ref name=nrao20090105/>。因為軌道速度取決於軌道半徑內的總質量，使推測銀河系有更大的質量，大約與仙女座星系相當，在距離中心{{convert|160000|ly|kpc|abbr=on}}的距離內，質量是7{{e|11}} {{solar mass}}<ref name="reid2009"/>。在2010年，測量暈星的徑向速度，發現在8,000[[秒差距|秒差距]]內的質量是7{{e|11}} {{solar mass}}<ref name="gnedin2010"/>。根據2014年發表的一項研究，銀河系的總質量估計為8.5{{e|11}} {{solar mass}}<ref name="Jorge Peñarrubia2014">{{cite journal
    | display-authors=1
    | first1=Jorge | last1=Peñarrubia
    | first2=Yin-Zhe | last2=Ma
    | first3=Matthew G. | last3=Walker
    | first4=Alan | last4=McConnachie
    | title=A dynamical model of the local cosmic expansion
    | journal=Monthly Notices of the Royal Astronomical Society
    | volume=433
    | issue=3
    | pages=2204–2022
    | bibcode= 2014MNRAS.443.2204P
    | doi=10.1093/mnras/stu879 | arxiv=1405.0306 }}</ref>，這大約是仙女座星系一半的質量<ref name="Jorge Peñarrubia2014" />。

銀河系的許多質量似乎是看不見且形式未知，但能和普通物質有引力交互作用的[[暗物質|暗物質]]。[[暗物質暈|暗物質暈]]相對均勻的分佈至距離銀河中心10萬秒差距處。銀河系的數學模型表明暗物質的質量是1–1.5{{e|12}} {{solar mass}}<ref name=McMillan2011/><ref name=McMillan2016/><ref>{{cite journal|author=Slobodan Ninković |title=Mass Distribution and Gravitational Potential of the Milky Way |journal=[[開放天文學|Open Astronomy]] |volume=26 |date=April 2017 |pages=1–6 |doi=10.1515/astro-2017-0002 |url=https://www.degruyter.com/view/j/astro.2017.26.issue-1/astro-2017-0002/astro-2017-0002.xml?format=INT |deadurl=no |archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20170422061853/https://www.degruyter.com/view/j/astro.2017.26.issue-1/astro-2017-0002/astro-2017-0002.xml?format=INT |archivedate=2017-04-22 }}</ref>。最近的研究表明質量範圍可以大到4.5{{e|12}} {{solar mass}} <ref>{{cite journal | display-authors=1 | last1=Phelps | first1=Steven | last2=Nusser | first2=Adi | last3=Desjacques | first3=Vincent | title=The Mass of the Milky Way and M31 Using the Method of Least Action | journal=The Astrophysical Journal | volume=775 | issue=2 | id=102 | pages=12 | date=October 2013 | doi=10.1088/0004-637X/775/2/102 | bibcode=2013ApJ...775..102P | arxiv=1306.4013 }}</ref>，小到8{{e|11}} {{solar mass}}<ref>{{cite journal | display-authors=1 | last1=Kafle | first1=Prajwal Raj | last2=Sharma | first2=Sanjib | last3=Lewis | first3=Geraint F. | last4=Bland-Hawthorn | first4=Joss | title=On the Shoulders of Giants: Properties of the Stellar Halo and the Milky Way Mass Distribution | journal=The Astrophysical Journal | volume=794 | issue=1 | id=59 | pages=17 | date=October 2014 | doi=10.1088/0004-637X/794/1/59 | bibcode=2014ApJ...794...59K | arxiv=1408.1787 }}</ref>。

銀河系所有恆星的總值量估計在4.6{{e|10}} {{solar mass}} <ref name="Licquia2013">{{cite journal
    | last1=Licquia | first1=Timothy | last2=Newman | first2=J.
    | title=Improved Constraints on the Total Stellar Mass, Color, and Luminosity of the Milky Way
    | journal=American Astronomical Society, AAS Meeting #221, #254.11
    | date=2013
    | bibcode=2013AAS...22125411L
    | doi=}}</ref>至6.43{{e|10}} {{solar mass}}之間<ref name="McMillan2011" />。除了恆星之外，還有包括90%的[[氫|氫]]和10%的[[氦|氦]]組成的星際氣體<ref name="ism1" />，其中三分之二的氫是[[21公分線|原子形式]]，其餘的三分之一是分子氫<ref name="ism2" />。這些氣體的質量相當於星系恆星總質量的10%<ref name="ism2">{{cite web |title=Lecture Seven: The Milky Way: Gas |url=http://www.astro.rug.nl/~etolstoy/pog14/resources/lectures/PoG-lecture7pr.pdf |accessdate=2015-05-02 |deadurl=yes |archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20150708011238/http://www.astro.rug.nl/~etolstoy/pog14/resources/lectures/PoG-lecture7pr.pdf |archivedate=2015-07-08 }}</ref>至15% <ref name="ism1">{{cite web |title=The Interstellar Medium |url=http://csep10.phys.utk.edu/astr162/lect/milkyway/ism.html |accessdate=2015-05-02 |deadurl=yes |archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20150419065745/http://csep10.phys.utk.edu/astr162/lect/milkyway/ism.html |archivedate=2015-04-19 }}</ref>。額外的[[星際塵埃|星際塵埃]]佔氣體總質量的1%<ref name="ism1" />。

== 容量 ==
{{Further|系外行星}}

銀河系包含的恆星數量在2,000億至4,000億顆之間<ref name=frommert_kronberg2005/><ref name=wethington2010/>，還有至少1,000億顆的行星<ref name=villard20120111/>。確切的數值取決於質量非常低的恆星，這些恆星很難被檢測得到，特別是距離太陽超過{{convert|300|ly|pc|-1|abbr=on}}的。作為比較，鄰近的仙女座星系估計擁有1兆（10<sup>12</sup>）顆恆星<ref name=young2006/>。填充在恆星之間空間的，是被稱為[[星際介質|星際介質]]的氣體和塵埃盤面。這個盤面的半徑至少相當程度的對應於恆星盤面的半徑<ref name=science312_1773/>，而氣體層的厚度從冷氣體的數百光年至熱氣體的數千光年<ref name=araa28_215/><ref name=apj702_1472/>。

在銀河系的恆星盤面，沒有在之外就沒有恆星的明確邊界。相對的，恆星的密度隨著與銀河中心距離的增加而遞減。大約在距離中心40,000光年（13,000秒差距），每立方秒差距的恆星數量掉落得比半徑的增加還快，而其原因還不了解<ref name=arxiv0909.3857/>。環繞在星系盤面周圍的是球狀的[[星系暈|星系暈]]和恆星組成的[[球狀星團|球狀星團]]，並進一步的向外延伸，但大小受到兩個銀河的衛星星系，大、小[[麥哲倫雲|麥哲倫雲]]的限制，它們的[[拱點|最接近]]銀河中心的距離大約是{{convert|180000|ly|kpc|abbr=on}}。因此，這些物體可能是從銀河系的附近被逐出的。綜合銀河系的[[絕對星等|絕對視星等]]被估計大約是 -20.9等<ref name=coffey/><ref name="Karachentsev2004">{{cite journal
    | last1=Karachentsev | first1=Igor D.
    | last2=Karachentseva | first2=Valentina E.
    | last3=Huchtmeier | first3=Walter K.
    | last4=Makarov | first4=Dmitry I.
    | title=A Catalog of Neighboring Galaxies
    | journal=The Astronomical Journal
    | year=2003
    | volume=127
    | issue=4
    | pages=2031–2068
    | bibcode = 2004AJ....127.2031K
    | doi = 10.1086/382905 }}</ref>{{NoteTag|name="milky way mag"}}。

經由[[微引力透鏡|微引力透鏡]]和觀測行星凌日，顯示在銀河系內的恆星有許多有多顆行星<ref name="Nature-20120111"/><ref name=borenstein2011/>，微引力透鏡的測量更顯示不被綁定的[[流浪行星|流浪行星]]比綁定行星的宿主恆星還要多<ref>{{cite journal | display-authors=1| last1 = Sumi | first1 = T. | last2 = Kamiya | first2 = K. | last3 = Bennett | first3 = D. P. | last4 = Bond | first4 = I. A. | last5 = Abe | first5 = F. | last6 = Botzler | first6 = C. S. | last7 = Fukui | first7 = A. | last8 = Furusawa | first8 = K. | last9 = Hearnshaw | first9 = J. B. | last10 = Itow | first10 = Y.| last11 = Kilmartin | first11 = P. M.| last12 = Korpela | first12 = A.| last13 = Lin | first13 = W.| last14 = Ling | first14 = C. H.| last15 = Masuda | first15 = K.| last16 = Matsubara | first16 = Y.| last17 = Miyake | first17 = N.| last18 = Motomura | first18 = M.| last19 = Muraki | first19 = Y.| last20 = Nagaya | first20 = M.| last21 = Nakamura | first21 = S.| last22 = Ohnishi | first22 = K.| last23 = Okumura | first23 = T.| last24 = Perrott | first24 = Y. C.| last25 = Rattenbury | first25 =  N.| last26 = Saito | first26 = To.| last27 = Sako | first27 = T.| last28 = Sullivan | first28 = D. J.| last29 = Sweatman | first29 = W. L.| last30 = Tristram | first30 = P. J.| last31 = Udalski | first31 = A.| last32 = Szymański | first32 = M. K.| last33 = Kubiak | first33 = M.| last34 = Pietrzyński | first34 =  G.| last35 = Poleski | first35 = R.| last36 = Soszyński | first36 = I.| last37 = Wyrzykowski | first37 = Ł.| last38 = Ulaczyk | first38 = K.| doi = 10.1038/nature10092 | title = Unbound or distant planetary mass population detected by gravitational microlensing | journal = Nature | volume = 473 | issue = 7347 | pages = 349–352 | year = 2011 | bibcode = 2011Natur.473..349S| arxiv = 1105.3544| pmid =  21593867| pmc = }}</ref><ref name=nasa20110526/>。銀河系的每顆恆星至少擁有一顆行星，就會有1,000億至4,000億顆行星；依據[[克卜勒太空望遠鏡|克卜勒太空望遠鏡]]在2013年1月的研究，顯示[[克卜勒32|克卜勒32]]有5顆行星<ref name="Space-20130102" />。分析克卜勒在2013年1月的不同資料，估計在銀河系中至少有170億顆[[類地行星|地球大小]]的[[系外行星|系外行星]] <ref name="Space-Billions">{{cite web |author=Staff |title=17 Billion Earth-Size Alien Planets Inhabit Milky Way |url=http://www.space.com/19157-billions-earth-size-alien-planets-aas221.html |date=2013-01-07 |publisher=[[Space.com|Space.com]] |accessdate=2013-01-08 |archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20141006095334/http://www.space.com/19157-billions-earth-size-alien-planets-aas221.html |archivedate=2014-10-06}}</ref>。在2013年11月4日，天文學家報告，基於[[克卜勒太空望遠鏡|克卜勒太空望遠鏡]]的資料，在銀河系的[[類太陽恆星|類太陽恆星]]和[[紅矮星|紅矮星]]的[[適居帶|適居帶]]內，可能有多達400億顆地球大小的[[系外行星|行星]]環繞著<ref name="NYT-20131104">{{cite news |last=Overbye |first=Dennis |title=Far-Off Planets Like the Earth Dot the Galaxy |url=https://www.nytimes.com/2013/11/05/science/cosmic-census-finds-billions-of-planets-that-could-be-like-earth.html |date=2013-11-04 |work=[[New_York_Times|New York Times]] |accessdate=2013-11-05 |deadurl=no |archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20131105023653/http://www.nytimes.com/2013/11/05/science/cosmic-census-finds-billions-of-planets-that-could-be-like-earth.html |archivedate=2013-11-05 }}</ref><ref name="PNAS-20131031">{{cite journal |last1=Petigura |first1=Eric A. |last2=Howard |first2=Andrew W. |last3=Marcy |first3=Geoffrey W. |title=Prevalence of Earth-size planets orbiting Sun-like stars |url = http://www.pnas.org/content/early/2013/10/31/1319909110 |date=2013-10-31 |journal=[[Proceedings_of_the_National_Academy_of_Sciences_of_the_United_States_of_America|Proceedings of the National Academy of Sciences of the United States of America]] |doi=10.1073/pnas.1319909110 |accessdate=2013-11-05 |arxiv=1311.6806 |bibcode=2013PNAS..11019273P |volume=110 |pages=19273–19278 |pmid=24191033 |pmc=3845182 |deadurl=no |archiveurl = https://web.archive.org/web/20131109010831/http://www.pnas.org/content/early/2013/10/31/1319909110 |archivedate=2013-11-09 }}</ref><ref name="nov2013_planet_estimate"/>。估計可能有110億顆行星環繞著類似太陽的恆星運行<ref name="LATimes-20131104">{{cite news |last=Khan |first=Amina |title=Milky Way may host billions of Earth-size planets |url = http://www.latimes.com/science/la-sci-earth-like-planets-20131105,0,2673237.story |date=2013-11-04 |work=[[Los_Angeles_Times|Los Angeles Times]] |accessdate=2013-11-05 |deadurl=no |archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20131106030558/http://www.latimes.com/science/la-sci-earth-like-planets-20131105%2C0%2C2673237.story |archivedate=2013-11-06 }}</ref>。2016年的研究顯示，最接近的這類行星可能就在距離4.2光年之處<ref name="Planet-Alpha-Centauri">{{cite journal |last=Anglada-Escudé | first= Guillem |coauthors = et. al. |title=A terrestrial planet candidate in a temperate orbit around Proxima Centauri | year=2016 | journal=Nature| volume=536 |pages=437–440 |doi=10.1038/nature19106 | pmid=27558064 }}</ref>。類似地球大小的行星可能比氣態巨行星更多<ref name="Nature-20120111" />。除了系外行星，也發現了在太陽系之外[[系外彗星|系外彗星]]，[[彗星|彗星]]在銀河系中可能也很常見<ref name="Space-Exocomets">{{cite web |author=Staff |title='Exocomets' Common Across Milky Way Galaxy |url = http://www.space.com/19156-exocomets-alien-solar-systems.html |date=2013-01-07 |publisher=[[Space.com|Space.com]] |accessdate=2013-01-08 |archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20140916085824/http://www.space.com/19156-exocomets-alien-solar-systems.html |archivedate=2014-09-16 }}</ref>。

