== 結構 ==
[[File:Artist's_impression_of_the_Milky_Way.ogv|thumb]]
{{multiple image
| align     = right
| direction = vertical
| width     = 220
| image1 =
| caption1 = 新銀河系圖展示四條清晰明確且相當對稱的旋臂 <ref name=sciamerica_20200401/>
| image2    = Artist's impression of the Milky Way (updated - annotated).jpg
| alt1      =
| caption2  = 藝術家想像的銀河系結構。有兩條主旋臂從核球的短棒向外延伸。  <ref name=two_arms />
